erity":"low","file":"src/core/step/custom-reviewer.ts","title":"writes() で宣言出力が確定済み","rationale":"custom reviewer は writes() で customReviewerResultPath を単一宣言している。scoped staging の union 計算に必要な declared outputs は既存機構で取得可能。"}]},"followUpAttempts":1,"transientRetryAttempts":0},"startedAt":"2026-07-13T20:03:52.720Z","endedAt":"2026-07-13T20:09:14.082Z"}
